      <title>摩根大通的马哈拉吉：对风险资产仍“相当乐观”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-06/jpm-s-maharaj-still-pretty-positive-on-risk-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通资产管理公司(JPMorgan Asset Management)多资产解决方案策略师图什卡·马哈拉吉(Thushka Maharaj)解释了她目前的资产配置，并表示她在持有股票和信贷市场等风险资产时“更有选择性”。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-06/jpm-s-maharaj-still-pretty-positive-on-risk-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 08:54:37 GMT</pubDate>
